dialog_1.name: Sister
dialog_1.text: You seem pretty excited. How was Orchard Theatre?

dialog_2.name: Sister
dialog_2.text: Sounds great! I should visit there sometime soon.

dialog_3.name: Sister
dialog_3.text: Now that you have the film, you will need to go develop it. Here is $0.05 for the development

dialog_4.name: Sister
dialog_4.text: Macdonald House nearby have a lot of photography shop. Maybe you can go take a look.
